image generation using genetic algorithms
============================================

About :
-------

this project is to generate a 100x100 pixel image similar to  a given image using genetic algorithm.
it uses 100 values to represent a image and a population of 100 value sets (chromosomes) to run
the algorithm with 100% crossover rate and 2% mutation rate. 

Running :
----------

This script is written in python. Install 'python' and 'Tkinter' to run the script. (use synaptic package
manager in Ubuntu to install them).

then use command ,

	python main.py

to run.

